{"tid":1788142,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"1222 東突厥斯坦國歌","createTime":"2019-12-18T12:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T06:30:06.000Z","uid":251732,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3db3ebeee1f02d307eeae2d52c2b9a520f1e1756","tid":1788142,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:12:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cssWeP_iPXU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcssWeP_iPXU&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6qVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=f83175b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cssWeP_iPXU</a><br />\n<br />\nQurtulush Marshi  獨立進行曲<br />\n<br />\nQurtulush yolida sudek aqti bizning qanimiz<br />\nSen &uuml;ch&uuml;n ey yurtumiz, bolsun fida bu janimiz<br />\nQan kechip hem jan berip, axir qurtuldurduq seni<br />\nQurtquzushqa qelbimizde bar idi imanimiz<br />\n<br />\nYurtumuz biz y&uuml;z k&ouml;z&uuml;ngni qan bilen pakizleduq<br />\nEmdi hich kirletmegeymiz, ch&uuml;nki T&uuml;rktur namimizYaru hemdem boldi bizning himmetimiz sen &uuml;ch&uuml;n<br />\nDunyani soraghan idi himmet bilen ejdadimiz<br />\n<br />\nAtalarning jengleri &ouml;chmeydu tarix betidinNesli qaldi jenggawer, biz uning ewladi biz<br />\nChiqti jan hem aqti qan, boldi yawdin el aman<br />\nYashasun hich &ouml;lmesun g&uuml;zel istiqbalimiz<br />\nYashasun, ming yashasun, parlansun istiqbalimiz<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIn the road to salvation was our blood spilled like water,<br />\n<br />\nFor you, oh Fatherland, may our lifes be a sacrifice<br />\n<br />\nWe saved you by dying and spilling our blood for you,<br />\n<br />\nWe had faith in our hearts for your liberty<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nOur hard work is for you,<br />\n<br />\nOur ancestors have once ruled the world.<br />\n<br />\nI cleansed you with blood, oh Fatherland,<br />\n<br />\nMay it never be spoiled again because Turk is our name.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAttila, Genghis and Tamerlane, once trembled the world,<br />\n<br />\nBy giving blood and earning honour, we are their children.<br />\n<br />\nWe gave our lives, spilled our blood and had our revenge from the enemy<br />\n<br />\nMay our future shine and prosper for eternity."},{"pid":"7a6f1f2ebf4bcdb447331996a688c76bc9c86567","tid":1788142,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"6712db02194bf8867404bbbdbd75e3500567b784","tid":1788142,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:43:44.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"8bf5348b53c0dfcada6299723c7c35ea6f1e043c","tid":1788142,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"push 3"},{"pid":"06ce02911a930afc1ca9348ddc050289eae508ca","tid":1788142,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"關香港咩事？"},{"pid":"cd0cd9d4180af5829ce4c8effa8f485882c296b7","tid":1788142,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ce02911a930afc1ca9348ddc050289eae508ca","tid":1788142,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"關香港咩事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"起碼你喺現場播呢首歌connect埋更多維吾爾族人"},{"pid":"9f38e7ba4d4482a5ec425bc9a65db5dabcdec0bb","tid":1788142,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ce02911a930afc1ca9348ddc050289eae508ca","tid":1788142,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"關香港咩事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用下你個閪腦唸野啦小朋友</span>"},{"pid":"d3a849f63ed906e32808ada43f2f5f8d9924774e","tid":1788142,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd0cd9d4180af5829ce4c8effa8f485882c296b7","tid":1788142,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ce02911a930afc1ca9348ddc050289eae508ca","t